T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"是旦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d騎呢運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩跆拳空手，全部都睇得唔打得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空手道，掂下就當打到<br />\n跆拳道，鬥體操咩家陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"乜柒都是但<br />\n香港只會更加垃圾"},{"pid":"e138ee9dcb60861b44cd836e24881f90ee063ca0","tid":602526,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"剩係知上次派人出賽都唔係睇成績就知幾黑暗啦"},{"pid":"30cfc85ef2aa138e4bf5245c40e163e191bf9c22","tid":602526,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ecQtY89TaLY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DecQtY89TaLY&d=0ukGSjiNL14Cx8Un7%2B1nc5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=45ce9093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ecQtY89TaLY</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】空手道界爆雪藏運動員風波！5名空手道精英運動員因不同理由轉換訓練道場，受空手道總會實施冷凍期，喪失全年國際大賽的選拔和參賽資格；有職業運動員更因而被踢出體育學院，訓練和資助被中斷。有受影響運動員家屬質疑決定違反奧委會約章，埋怨政府及體院零監管，計劃提告要求空總撤銷冷凍期規定。<br />\n記者：龔蕙芝、張軍、阮斌、黃學潤"},{"pid":"bca32091ad8da4b7dff82a24e7301b473cc2addf","tid":602526,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"香港應該搞 MMA,  全民搏擊大賽先好玩"},{"pid":"d159fe2f551e9465ccd10b6c6b623c937dc7608f","tid":602526,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}